### ğŸŸ¢ Distributionally Robust Optimization

In **DRO**, we optimize against the worst-case distribution within an ambiguity set.  
I am especially interested in:
- duality-based formulations,
- Wasserstein-based sets,
- and connections with learning theory.

> ğŸ“˜ *Suggested readings:*
> - *"Distributionally Robust Optimization: A Review" â€“ Rahimian & Mehrotra*
> - *"Robust Optimization" â€“ Ben-Tal, El Ghaoui & Nemirovski*

